Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: gh-utils-lenik
Architecture: all
Depends: git (>= 1:2), gh, bash-shlib, ${misc:Depends}
Description: GitHub CLI helper tools
 This package provides:
 .
  * gh-refresh-contributors: temporarily renames the repository default branch
    (e.g. main or master) to a temporary name and renames it back, which
    triggers GitHub to refresh the repository contributors list on the web
    interface.
  * gh-release: creates a GitHub release from the version in debian/changelog,
    including a source tarball and release notes from the changelog.
 .
 Requires a GitHub CLI (gh) authenticated session and a git repo with
 remote "origin" pointing to the GitHub repository.
